title: tokyohd
author: tokyohd
content: Dogecoin's latest performance was a nice surprise for investors, as the coin successfully broke through resistance levels that U.Today mentioned previously. As of now, DOGE is on its way to breaking even stronger barriers. At press time, DOGE was getting close to the 50-day Exponential Moving Average and showed the potential of breaking through it as the trading volume saw a strong spike in the first day of the trading week. Full Details: https://u.today/dogecoin-doge-becomes-most-profitable-asset-on-market-with-13-price-increase
